summary: This is a modders resource of new ingots, ores and forge resources I have put together. It comes with an esp file with all the resources added as statics with a suffix of LYKS. I will also be adding more resources to this mod as I create them...
descriptionHtml: I have created a new modders resource that as I make resources for will be added too... These will be only smithing items like ingots and ores. So far I have made a whole set of new extra large ingot stacks. These are just regular ingot textures and meshes!! I have also started creating new super ingot stacks. These are done with the new meshes and textures I have put together and included with this resource... I have included a few new ores and textures to go with them as well. Now these new super ingot stacks take awhile to make so just be patient...
